reviewText: If you are considering this movie for length or its apparent subject. Do not buy it, rather go listen to Felix Da Housecat and you will be better edified. It is and remains a veritable waste of anyone's time. Period
This is a Great Film!!! I never laughed so hard in my life i thought weeding crashers was great but now this is my new all time favorite movie!! Gosh i hoping they make more of these!!!!

Never have I seen something so funny that simultaneously had me looking over my shoulder to see if I was being monitored by homeland security.  If you're looking for something different and a winner, this is definitely for you.
